title: Something About a Family Photo
description: When they plan to take a family photo for their Christmas cards. Jack wants to wear his favorite sweater but it's still at his dry cleaner which is clear across town. So Carly tells him that he should find one closer to home. So when he goes to see him and tells him his plans he refuses to give him the sweater without the ticket which Jack never needed.
